item.title: Rust Disassembly: part 1
item.description: What do some Rust features compile to? Intro I have been starting to have a look at Rust lately, mostly because WASM is growing on me and Rust has the best tool in class for it, or so I am told. I am eager to find out by myself. Rust comes with several new idioms and structures in the language I am not used to, and being a performance enthusiast, I always get interested in what such constructs translate to.
